---
id: chickpea-greek-bowl
title: Chickpea Greek Bowl
description: A no-cook bowl with chickpeas, cucumber, tomatoes, feta, and quinoa.
servings: 2
mealTypes: [lunch, dinner]
tags: [vegetarian, no-cook]
prep time: 15 minutes
cook time: 0 minutes
---

Rinse @chickpeas{1%can} in a #colander{}.

Chop @cucumber{1} and @cherry tomatoes{1%cup} on a #cutting board{}.

Combine chickpeas, vegetables, @feta cheese{1/2%cup}, @cooked quinoa{1%cup}, and @Greek dressing{2%tbsp} in a #mixing bowl{}.
